comments: Zeller (CHA) places his hand momentarily on Adebayo's (MIA) hip before he removes his hand.
Adebayo (MIA) is in the lane for longer than three seconds.
Zeller (CHA) impedes Adebayo (MIA) and restricts his ability to retrieve the rebound.
Butler (MIA) braces for the contact with Monk (CHA) and keeps his off-arm collapsed against his body without extending.
Zeller (CHA) and Butler (MIA) make incidental contact with one another during rebounding.
Hayward (CHA) brushes Butler's (MIA) arm at the end of his drive, and contact is marginal.
Ball (CHA) is already in Herro's (MIA) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Iguodala (MIA) extends his forearm into Graham's (CHA) body and affects his driving shot attempt.
Hayward (CHA) is moving alongside Butler's (MIA) path and maintains a legal guarding position as he defends the drive to the basket.
Herro (MIA) is moving alongside Graham's (CHA) path and maintains a legal guarding position.
Zeller (CHA) is already in Butler's (MIA) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Zeller (CHA) is already in Iguodala's (MIA) path and is firming up when contact occurs.
Adebayo (MIA) legally contests Monk's (CHA) jump shot attempt.  Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Hayward (CHA) legally contests Butler's (MIA) jump shot attempt.
